# Agent Project State (last updated: 2026-06-16)

## Architecture Summary

- **Vercel (Next.js 14):** 176 API routes — ERP + agent UI + internal worker endpoints
- **VPS Worker (31.97.237.40):** BullMQ + 47 cron schedulers + Telegram bot
- **Auth:** Worker→Vercel uses `Bearer AGENT_INTERNAL_TOKEN`. UI uses NextAuth session.
- **Middleware bypass:** `/api/agent/*`, `/api/assistant/internal/*`, `/api/assistant/chat`, `/api/assistant/conversations`, `/api/assistant/todos`, and action approve/reject paths pass through with Bearer token.

## What's Working (verified 2026-06-16)

### Scheduler (SCHEDULERS_ENABLED=true on VPS — confirmed active)
- 47 cron jobs registered and running
- Morning: owner-briefing (07:30), todo-reminder (08:00), strategist (08:00), staff-dispatch (09:00)
- Midday: staff-presence (11:00/17:00), morale (13:00), midday-checkin (13:30)
- Evening: todo-summary (20:30), night-report (21:00), evening-proposal (21:05), daily-summary (23:30)
- Continuous: salah-escalation (5min), proof-timeout (5min), auto-fix-scan (15min), cs-escalation (1min)

### Intelligence Features (all wired to worker)
- `/api/agent/trust-check` → `staff-approval-gate.mjs` (auto/notify/approve tiers)
- `/api/agent/staff-context` → `dispatch.mjs` (contextual Bangla greetings)
- `/api/agent/staff-capabilities` → `evening-proposal.mjs` (skill profiles)
- `/api/agent/smart-task` → `evening-proposal.mjs` (AI task briefs with difficulty levels)
- `/api/agent/health-scan` → `error-collector.mjs` (dual auth: Bearer + session)

### Agent Todo System
- `agent_todos` Prisma model in DB
- `/api/assistant/todos` — CRUD, dual auth (Bearer + session)
- `AgentTodoPanel` component on agent homepage
- `manage_work_todos` agent tool (list/add/update/complete/summary)
- `todo-reminder.mjs` scheduler: morning 08:00 + evening 20:30 Telegram messages
- System prompt includes todo-driven daily workflow instructions

### Long Agent Tasks
- `long_agent_task` BullMQ processor implemented — calls `/api/assistant/chat` with 5-min timeout

## VPS Deploy Process
- SSH: `root@31.97.237.40`, repo at `/opt/alma-erp`, PM2 process: `agent-worker`
- From ERP: Staff Monitor → Deploy Worker button
- Direct: `cd /opt/alma-erp && git pull origin main && cd worker && npm ci --omit=dev && pm2 restart agent-worker --update-env`

## Known Patterns & Gotchas
- Vercel `env pull` shows AGENT_INTERNAL_TOKEN as empty (encrypted) — use VPS .env directly
- Middleware blocks non-internal paths even if route handler has Bearer auth — must add to `isAssistantWorkerBypassPath()` in `src/lib/agent-internal-auth.ts`
- Local `next build` exits 1 due to missing DATABASE_URL — expected, Vercel has it
- PWA service worker can cache stale builds — users may need hard refresh after deploy

